It’s Not Just Estrogen — Why Midlife Weight Feels So Stubborn

If you’ve hit your 40s or 50s and noticed the scales creeping up — even when you haven’t changed a thing — you’re not alone.


The truth? Four key hormones naturally shift during midlife: estrogen, progesterone, cortisol, and insulin. When these changes happen, they can influence how your body uses energy, how motivated you feel to move, and even how easy it is to stick to healthy habits.


Most “solutions” focus on just one of these areas. But if you want to feel your best again, you need an approach that supports all four.


That’s why we created Hormone Balance — a blend of 8 carefully chosen nutrients and botanicals designed to complement your body’s natural processes, support energy, and help you feel comfortable and confident in your own skin.

Key Researched-backed ingredients

Our formula supports the four critical pillars of hormonal health — estrogen, progesterone, cortisol, and insulin — using clinically studied nutrients and powerful plant extracts.

Hormone Balance & Menopause Support

Soya Bean Extract (providing Isoflavones), Sage, and Hops are combined to help maintain natural hormonal activity, supporting comfort during menopause and easing common symptoms.

Mind, Focus & Resilience

Panax Ginseng, Rosemary Leaf, and Vitamin B6 support normal psychological function, while Vitamin B12 contributes to normal energy-yielding metabolism — helping you stay focused and ready to take on the day.

Bone, Muscle & Energy Support

Calcium, Vitamin D, and Magnesium contribute to the maintenance of normal bones and muscle function. Vitamin B6 and Zinc support normal energy metabolism, helping you feel prepared for your daily activities.

Metabolism & Balanced Energy

Flaxseed, Kelp, and Alfalfa deliver plant-based nutrients that work alongside Vitamin B6 to support normal energy release and macronutrient metabolism. A balanced metabolism can help you feel more in control of weight management as part of a healthy diet and active lifestyle.
